<div class="relative p-12 mx-auto text-golfsnack-800">
  <input class="w-full h-10 px-4 py-8 text-sm bg-white border-2 rounded-lg placeholder-golfsnack-500 border-wetsand-300 focus:outline-none"
          type="search" name="search" placeholder="Sök">
  <button type="submit" class="absolute mt-5 mr-4 right-11 top-11">
    <svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-current text-golfsnack-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" id="Capa_1" x="0px" y="0px"
            viewBox="0 0 56.966 56.966" style="enable-background:new 0 0 56.966 56.966;" xml:space="preserve"
            width="512px" height="512px">
      <path
              d="M55.146,51.887L41.588,37.786c3.486-4.144,5.396-9.358,5.396-14.786c0-12.682-10.318-23-23-23s-23,10.318-23,23  s10.318,23,23,23c4.761,0,9.298-1.436,13.177-4.162l13.661,14.208c0.571,0.593,1.339,0.92,2.162,0.92  c0.779,0,1.518-0.297,2.079-0.837C56.255,54.982,56.293,53.08,55.146,51.887z M23.984,6c9.374,0,17,7.626,17,17s-7.626,17-17,17  s-17-7.626-17-17S14.61,6,23.984,6z" />
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container px-12 mx-auto ">
  <div class="grid w-full gap-4 pb-12 mb-12 border-b sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 border-wetsand-300">
    <img class="object-cover w-full" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580758852857-a243f4de9cc7?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="">
    <div class="col-span-3 md:border-r border-wetsand-200 md:pr-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full title">
        <div class="flex">
          <h1 class="mr-2">KOBERG GOLFKLUBB</h1>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-500">
            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
          </svg>
          <h4>7,4</h4>
        </div>
        <strong class="mb-2">TROLLHÄTTAN</strong>
        <div class="text-columns">
          <p>Mind where the divot lands! Completely missed the ball, oops! Steady footwork Cheating on the next hole For packing in golf Dancing on the practise ground. Mind where the divot lands! Pull out your 3-wood and.... Pull out your 3-wood and.... Brassie Get a new Sand Iron Dip your opponents grips in sticky paste, Pitch and run.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h5>INFO</h5>
      <dl>
        <dt>Antal hål:</dt>
        <dd>18</dd>
        <dt>Par</dt>
        <dd>73</dd>
        <dt>Längd</dt>
        <dd>5300 m</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h4 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-thin uppercase text-golfsnack-500">SENAST SPELADE</h4>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-around gap-8 mb-12">
    <% @clubs[0..4].each do |club| %>
      <div class="relative flex flex-col xs:w-1/2 sm:w-1/4 md:w-1/6">
        <% if current_user.avatar.attached? %>
          <%= image_tag current_user.avatar.variant(resize_to_fill: [40, 25], gravity: 'center'), class: 'mini-avatar absolute -top-2 -left-2' %>
        <% else %>
          <%= image_tag "fallback/avatar-thumb-default.png", class: 'small-avatar' %>
        <% end %>
        <img class="object-cover w-full " src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543943475-e50600c4e81c?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8MXx8Z29sZiUyMGNvdXJzZXxlbnwwfHwwfA%3D%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&h=400&q=60" alt="">
        <div class="flex justify-between">
          <h4 class="mt-2 text-xs uppercase text-golfsnack-400"><%= club.name%></h4>
          <span class="flex mt-2 text-xs text-golfsnack-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
            </svg>
            7,4
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-sand-200">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-xs font-medium leading-4 tracking-wider text-left uppercase bg-sand-50">
          Namn
        </th>
        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-xs font-medium leading-4 tracking-wider text-left uppercase bg-sand-50">
          Beskrivning
        </th>
        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-xs font-medium leading-4 tracking-wider text-left uppercase bg-sand-50">
          Medlemmar
        </th>
        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-xs font-medium leading-4 tracking-wider text-left uppercase bg-sand-50">
          Inlägg
        </th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-sand-200">
      <% @clubs.each do |club| %>
        <tr>
          <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap">
            <%= link_to club.name, club %>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-4">
            <%= club.description %>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-4">
            <%= club.users.size %>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-4">
            <%= club.posts.size %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <%= paginate @clubs %>
</div>
